Anthrax, Kazakhstan
-------------------
Information received on [and dated] 8 Aug 2016 from Dr Samat Tyulegenov, director general, RSE "National Reference Center for Veterinary", Ministry of Agriculture, ASTANA, Kazakhstan

Summary:
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 30 Jul 2016
Date of confirmation of the event: 2 Aug 2016
Reason for notification: reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 29 Jul 2016
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: _Bacillus anthracis_
Nature of diagnosis: laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country.

New outbreaks (1)
Outbreak 1: Nursai village, Terenkol, Mangyshlak [Mangghystau Region]
Date of start of the outbreak: 30 Jul 2016
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
Epidemiological unit: village
Affected animals:
